This paper discusses the challenges and proposes a solution for enhancing the reliability of service chains in 5G communication services. This topic falls under the category of computer networks and communication (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the possibility of network failures due to software issues, which can be categorized under computer security and cryptography (cs.CR). The proposed solution involves meeting service level agreements, which can be categorized under control systems (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the softwarization of network and service functions, which can be categorized under distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC) and software engineering (cs.SE).
